        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued July 6 at 1:27PM CDT until July 6 at 2:00PM CDT by NWS Hastings NE</headline>
        <description>SVRGID

The National Weather Service in Hastings has issued a

* Severe Thunderstorm Warning for...
Northern Greeley County in central Nebraska...

* Until 200 PM CDT.

* At 126 PM CDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 7 miles south of
Ericson, or 16 miles east of Ord, moving east at 25 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and penny size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Expect damage to roofs, siding, and trees.

* This severe thunderstorm will remain over mainly rural areas of
northern Greeley County.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
